### 📦 Get All Courses
GET {{url}}/courses/find
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 🔍 Get Course by ID
GET {{url}}/courses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 👨‍🏫 Get Courses by Instructor
GET {{url}}/courses/instructor?instructor_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
